      "node_spec": "node:\n  id: generation_error_issue\n  intent: The caller is reporting an issue with the clinic's generation process, such as a failed generation.\n  instructions: Apologize for the inconvenience and ask the caller to provide more details about the generation error they are experiencing, such as the type of generation or when it occurred. If the issue cannot be resolved, offer to transfer the caller to a human representative for further assistance. Be sure to empathize with the caller's frustration and provide a solution or alternative if possible.\n  tools: [\"get_generation_status\", \"send_error_report\"]\n  output_variables: [\"generation_error_details\", \"caller_contact_info\"]\n  edges:\n    - from: \"intent_classification\"\n      condition: \"intent == generation_error_issue\"\n    - to: \"anything_else\"\n      condition: \"issue_resolved == true\"",
